    {
      "start": 64.28,
      "end": 65.64,
      "text": "찐 패밀리까지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.4,
      "end": 68.08,
      "text": "어떤 방송이었을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.54,
      "end": 69.46,
      "text": "저도 궁금한데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.46,
      "end": 71.74,
      "text": "그러게요 워낙 활발하게 활동을 하고 계시니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.74,
      "end": 75.2,
      "text": "어떤 모습을 보셨는지도 나중에 알려주시면 좋겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.2,
      "end": 76.68,
      "text": "Do you know where that message is from?"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.84,
      "end": 77.34,
      "text": "Which city?"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.68,
      "end": 79.1,
      "text": "그거는 전 잘 모르겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.1,
      "end": 79.76,
      "text": "그건 모르겠고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.76,
      "end": 81.22,
      "text": "Anyway, thank you"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.22,
      "end": 82.34,
      "text": "네, 너무 감사합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.34,
      "end": 85.52,
      "text": "And 이제 영화의 내용을 알아볼 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.52,
      "end": 88.28,
      "text": "As I said before, this movie received more attention"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.28,
      "end": 89.46,
      "text": "because of some factors"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.46,
      "end": 93.7,
      "text": "That is, 이 영화가 여성 운동에 관한 영화이기도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.7,
      "end": 96.7,
      "text": "또 주인공들도 여성들이 대부분이고"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.7,
      "end": 99.94,
      "text": "또 감독도 여성이고 작가도 여성이라서"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.94,
      "end": 102.82,
      "text": "관심을 더 많이 받았다라는 이야기를 했었잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.82,
      "end": 103.7,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.7,
      "end": 104.82,
      "text": "What about these days?"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.82,
      "end": 107.88,
      "text": "Are women getting more power in the film industry these days?"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.08,
      "end": 110.94,
      "text": "I don't know if it's like they're taking more power"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.94,
      "end": 115.3,
      "text": "I think more and more women are just getting interested"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.3,
      "end": 117.0,
      "text": "or interested in this field"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.0,
      "end": 118.46,
      "text": "and they're going into this field"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.46,
      "end": 121.22,
      "text": "and Cara Knightley in an interview"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.22,
      "end": 122.48,
      "text": "she said"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.48,
      "end": 127.58,
      "text": "I find it really interesting that in this movie Misbehavior"
